=== 2015年至今：欧洲歌唱大赛和专辑《Perfectly Damaged》 ===

2015年，塞默洛第三次参加瑞典旋律节，演唱歌曲《[[英雄_(芒斯·塞默洛歌曲)|英雄們]]》，并以288分的成绩获得总决赛冠军，得以代表瑞典前往[[奥地利|奥地利]][[维也纳|维也纳]]参加[[2015年欧洲歌唱大赛|2015年欧洲歌唱大赛]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6027884|title=Saade and Zelmerlöw favourites for Melodifestivalen 2015|author=Sveriges Radio|accessdate=3 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103192506/http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6027884|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.trelleborgsallehanda.se/tt-feature/saade-och-zelmerlow-siktar-mot-seger/|title=Saade och Zelmerlöw siktar mot seger|author=TT|date=25 November 2014|work=Trelleborgs Allehanda|accessdate=3 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103195809/http://www.trelleborgsallehanda.se/tt-feature/saade-och-zelmerlow-siktar-mot-seger/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://esctoday.com/98229/sweden-mans-zelmerlow-wins-melodifestivalen-2015/|title=Eurovision Sweden: Måns Zelmerlöw wins Melodifestivalen 2015!|work=esctoday.com|accessdate=14 March 2015|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523235613/http://esctoday.com/98229/sweden-mans-zelmerlow-wins-melodifestivalen-2015|dead-url=no}}</ref>他还为同一比赛的参赛者贝朗·米利（Behrang Miri）创作了歌曲《Det rår vi inte för》，米利也凭借这首歌曲进入了复活赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.svt.se/melodifestivalen/det-rar-vi-inte-for-skrevs-for-mans-zelmerlow|title="Det rår vi inte för" skrevs för Måns Zelmerlöw|work=svt.se|accessdate=28 March 2015|archive-date=2015-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221185818/http://www.svt.se/melodifestivalen/det-rar-vi-inte-for-skrevs-for-mans-zelmerlow|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年5月21日，塞默洛参加了欧洲歌唱大赛的第二场预赛，并顺利进入决赛。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/mans-succe--till-final-i-esc-efter-nervpars/|title=Måns succé – till final i ESC efter nervpärs|work=Expressen|accessdate=21 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523172259/http://www.expressen.se/noje/mans-succe--till-final-i-esc-efter-nervpars/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurovision.tv/page/news?id=mans_zelmerloew_a_eurovision_hero_for_sweden|title=Måns Zelmerlöw, a Eurovision hero for Sweden|work=Eurovision.tv|accessdate=17 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518202142/http://www.eurovision.tv/page/news?id=mans_zelmerloew_a_eurovision_hero_for_sweden|dead-url=no}}</ref>在5月23日的总决赛中，塞默洛以365分的成绩获得总冠军。<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-32850671|title=Eurovision Song Contest: Sweden's Mans Zelmerlow wins|work=BBC News|accessdate=23 May 2015|archive-date=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221150525/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-32850671|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1489730/sweden-wins-eurovision-song-contest-2015|title=Sweden Wins Eurovision Song Contest 2015|work=Sky News|accessdate=23 May 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150524001419/http://news.sky.com/story/1489730/sweden-wins-eurovision-song-contest-2015|archivedate=2015年5月24日}}</ref>这也是瑞典在欧洲歌唱大赛历史上获得的第六个冠军。<ref name="#1"/>

2015年5月11日，塞默洛公布了自己第四张个人专辑《Perfectly Damaged》 的曲目列表和专辑封面，专辑将于同年6月5日发行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/manszelmerlow/status/597737691166420992|title="Måns Zelmerlöw at Twitter|work=twitter.com|accessdate=11 May 2015|archive-date=2016-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222125630/https://twitter.com/manszelmerlow/status/597737691166420992|dead-url=no}}</ref>

他还于2015年9月9—11日造访[[中华人民共和国|中国]][[上海市|上海]]，为他的新专辑宣传造势。

==个人生活==
塞默洛本人热爱[[足球|足球]]、[[网球|网球]]和[[高尔夫|高尔夫]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mzw.se/info.php?cat=2&subcat=7&lang=sv|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120729144007/http://www.mzw.se/info.php?cat=2&subcat=7&lang=sv|title=Måns Zelmerlöw – Biografi|archivedate=29 July 2012|publisher=|accessdate=21 March 2015|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2008年到2011年期间，他曾与瑞典歌手和模特兒{{le|玛丽·塞内霍尔特|Marie Serneholt}}有过一段恋情。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/klick/article13411990.ab|title=Måns Zelmerlöw och Marie Serneholt gjorde slut mitt under allsången: Vi är inte ett par längre – Klick!|work=Aftonbladet|accessdate=4 March 2015|archive-date=2017-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170805215434/http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/klick/article13411990.ab|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2004年12月26日，塞默洛和家人在[[泰国|泰国]]度假时曾遭遇[[2004年印度洋大地震|印度洋地震和海啸]]，而全家人都幸免于难。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/article14036895.ab|title=Måns Zelmerlöw var med om tsunamin 2004: Det var ofattbart hemskt – Nöjesbladet – Aftonbladet|work=Aftonbladet|accessdate=21 March 2015|archive-date=2018-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180401213354/https://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/article14036895.ab|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv4.se/efter-tio/klipp/m%C3%A5ns-zelmerl%C3%B6w-jag-gl%C3%B6mmer-aldrig-likstanken-3013101|title=Måns Zelmerlöw: "Jag glömmer aldrig likstanken" - Malou Efter tio – tv4.se|publisher=|accessdate=21 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104550/http://www.tv4.se/efter-tio/klipp/m%C3%A5ns-zelmerl%C3%B6w-jag-gl%C3%B6mmer-aldrig-likstanken-3013101|archivedate=2015年4月2日}}</ref>

2014年3月，塞默洛在出席一个瑞典烹饪节目时称[[同性恋|同性恋]]对他来说是“不正常的”（{{lang|sv|avvikelse}}），引发争议。<ref>{{cite web|title=SWEDEN: MÅNS ZELMERLÖW APOLOGISES AFTER GAY COMMENTS ON "PLURAS KÖK"|url=http://wiwibloggs.com/2014/03/23/sweden-mans-zelmerlow-homophobe/44030/|website=Wiwibloggs|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212205838/http://wiwibloggs.com/2014/03/23/sweden-mans-zelmerlow-homophobe/44030|archive-date=2018-02-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="independent.co.uk">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/eurovision-song-contest-2015-sweden-selects-singer-who-made-antigay-remarks-10110449.html|title=Eurovision Song Contest 2015: Sweden selects singer who made anti-gay remarks|work=The Independent|accessdate=16 March 2015|archive-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150709160800/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/eurovision-song-contest-2015-sweden-selects-singer-who-made-antigay-remarks-10110449.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后他多次向公众道歉，表示自己的言论有误，是沟通上的误会。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Larsson|first1=Ronny|title=Måns "Jag passerade gränsen på så många sätt"|url=http://www.qx.se/noje/gaygalan/27610/mans-jag-passerade-gransen-pa-sa-manga-satt|accessdate=20 March 2015|work=QX|date=3 November 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924084110/http://www.qx.se/noje/gaygalan/27610/mans-jag-passerade-gransen-pa-sa-manga-satt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Måns: Försökt att få den delen bortklippt|url=http://www.expressen.se/noje/mans-forsokt-att-fa-den-delen-bortklippt/|website=Expressen|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2018-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002064759/https://www.expressen.se/noje/mans-forsokt-att-fa-den-delen-bortklippt/|dead-url=no}}</ref>瑞典的[[LGBT|LGBT]]群体也认为他参加过众多LGBT平权活动，本身并非[[同性恋恐惧症|恐同]]人士，类似言论仅仅是误会所致。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Fahl|first1=Hanna|title=Is Måns Zelmerlöw A Homophobe FAQ!|url=http://blogg.dn.se/melodifestivalen2015/2015/03/16/is-mans-zelmerlow-a-homophobe-faq/|accessdate=20 March 2015|work=DN.se|date=16 March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320115831/http://blogg.dn.se/melodifestivalen2015/2015/03/16/is-mans-zelmerlow-a-homophobe-faq/|archivedate=2015年3月20日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Larsson|first1=Ronny|title=Comment: Swedish Eurovision star shouldn’t get nul points for his comments about gays|url=http://www.pinknews.co.uk/2015/03/18/comment-swedish-eurovision-star-shouldnt-get-nul-points-for-his-comments-about-gays/|accessdate=20 March 2015|work=Pink News|date=18 March 2015|archive-date=2019-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190103060916/https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2015/03/18/comment-swedish-eurovision-star-shouldnt-get-nul-points-for-his-comments-about-gays/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Adams|first1=William Lee|title=Måns Zelmerlöw: Melodifestivalen winner is not a homophobe MÅNS ZELMERLÖW: MELODIFESTIVALEN WINNER IS NOT A HOMOPHOBE|url=http://wiwibloggs.com/2015/03/16/mans-zelmerlow-melodifestivalen-homophobe/86590/|website=Wiwibloggs|publisher=Wiwibloggs|accessdate=20 March 2015|archive-date=2018-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180406210819/http://wiwibloggs.com/2015/03/16/mans-zelmerlow-melodifestivalen-homophobe/86590/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后他表示自己并不排斥与另一位男性交往。<ref>{{Cite news|title = Zelmerlöw: Kan tänka mig att dejta en kille|url = http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/article20776641.ab|accessdate = 2015-05-23|newspaper = [[Aftonbladet|Aftonbladet]]|date = 11 May 2015|first = Linn|last = Elmervik|archive-date = 2017-08-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170822181053/http://www.aftonbladet.se/nojesbladet/article20776641.ab|dead-url = no}}</ref>在获得欧洲歌唱大赛冠军之后，塞默洛也在获奖感言中表示：“无论我们与谁相爱，无论我们是谁，无论我们有怎样的信仰，我们都是英雄。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/05/23/eurovision-2015-winner-mans-zelmerlow-sweden|title=Sweden's Måns Zelmerlöw is 2015's Eurovision Song Contest winner|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2015-02-23|access-date=2015-05-24|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211212924/https://ew.com/article/2015/05/23/eurovision-2015-winner-mans-zelmerlow-sweden/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

